Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.62,0:00:04.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}要我离开这里？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.66,0:00:06.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这就是你的条件？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.58,0:00:07.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.41,0:00:13.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这与我已经立下的誓言相违背
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.33,0:00:14.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}请恕我不能答应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.41,0:00:16.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}如果他不答应
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.66,0:00:17.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不必纠缠
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.95,0:00:19.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}拿天明珠就是
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.70,0:00:20.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那我就要天明珠吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.12,0:00:22.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.50,0:00:25.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这绝不是你一时兴起提出的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:26.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是无限让你来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.91,0:00:29.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}替我谢谢他
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.70,0:00:36.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小白？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.20,0:00:39.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我能听懂耶！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.45,0:00:40.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}为什么呀！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.12,0:00:42.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是属于意识的传递~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.25,0:00:44.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好神奇~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.70,0:00:46.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那别人听不懂么？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.16,0:00:48.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}恩，传递的对象是由我决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:49.29,0:00:50.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好棒好棒这样好棒~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.70,0:00:54.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那以后考试小黑可以在窗外光明正大的给我报答案啦！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:55.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不是这么用的…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.58,0:00:56.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.20,0:00:58.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你们适应的很快嘛~
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.70,0:01:01.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑你的伤不要紧么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.66,0:01:02.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}没事了 ~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.54,0:01:13.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}爷爷~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.29,0:01:16.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}回来啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.58,0:01:18.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}唔？比丢也回来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.87,0:01:19.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}BIU!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.70,0:01:21.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不许晈房子啊T T
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.33,0:01:22.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈哈……
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}三叔好!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.16,0:01:24.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}几
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.45,0:01:24.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}几时
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.87,0:01:26.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}几时回来的？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.29,0:01:27.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}四天了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.41,0:01:27.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.54,0:01:28.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢噢噢
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.08,0:01:30.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}才四天么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:30.62,0:01:32.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我怎么感觉好久了？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.83,0:01:34.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是因为更新太慢了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.25,0:01:35.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}没什么
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.91,0:01:43.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑也是妖怪呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.87,0:01:44.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}幸会幸会
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.95,0:01:46.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}以后叫我小罗就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.08,0:01:48.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}爷爷…我比你小啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:48.33,0:01:49.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.08,0:01:50.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对了爷爷
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是老君给你的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.58,0:01:54.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哟哟要到啦~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.45,0:01:55.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}下次不许这样了啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.95,0:02:00.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我可以去拆村里的老君庙么…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.58,0:02:01.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不想理你们…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.33,0:02:03.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.87,0:02:04.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是地图
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.83,0:02:05.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我看看
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.29,0:02:08.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}在市里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.62,0:02:10.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是要我们去这里拿么？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.58,0:02:11.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不会是陷阱吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.70,0:02:12.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不会的啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.00,0:02:17.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小白，我们去做饭了，你先去洗澡吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.66,0:02:18.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好的~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.54,0:02:28.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好漂亮啊~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.41,0:02:30.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}像海一样
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.20,0:02:32.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是啊〜
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.25,0:02:33.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}过几天就会退掉了~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.83,0:02:35.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还好夏收已经结束了~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.29,0:02:42.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}明天开始
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.37,0:02:44.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我们就要训练比丢饮食咯
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.41,0:02:45.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}恩！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.75,0:02:47.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}比丢要听话噢~
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.45,0:02:51.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}比丢不是妖精
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.37,0:02:53.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}为什么会变大呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.20,0:02:55.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}妖精只是一种生物形成方式的称呼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.87,0:02:57.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}并不是因为他们能够操纵灵质
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.04,0:03:00.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}理论上来说所有生物都可以做到
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.04,0:03:02.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对哦…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.25,0:03:04.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君说过人类也可以当神的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:07.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那我也可以像哥哥一样控制水么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.45,0:03:08.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.16,0:03:09.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊，真的么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.54,0:03:10.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}怎么做呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.83,0:03:12.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你开始有兴趣了么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.16,0:03:12.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.08,0:03:14.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.54,0:03:15.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}在我们的周围呀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.20,0:03:17.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}有无数肉眼看不见的灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.00,0:03:19.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}无处不在
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.00,0:03:22.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}它们分为物质灵与生灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.75,0:03:24.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}生灵会自己汇聚
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.45,0:03:25.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}成为没有实体的精灵
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:30.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}精灵在不断吸收不断变化过程中与物质灵结合
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.66,0:03:33.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}演变成不同程度的实体
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.12,0:03:34.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这就是妖精了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.95,0:03:36.37,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}因为聚灵而生
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.50,0:03:39.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}所以妖精对灵的控制有先天优势
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.95,0:03:41.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}还记得老君的灵质空间么？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.95,0:03:42.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}嗯！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.66,0:03:44.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那是控制灵质的关键
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.41,0:03:47.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}修行会让灵质空间产生不同属性的变化
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.62,0:03:50.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那没有灵质空间是不是就不能修炼了？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.62,0:03:51.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}每个生命体都有的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.08,0:03:54.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}呼吸之间就已在吸取着生灵了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.62,0:03:58.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那为什么都没有见过有人像哥哥这样呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.83,0:04:00.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是由先天特性决定的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.54,0:04:03.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}给
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.12,0:04:03.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.95,0:04:05.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}好乖~
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.33,0:04:08.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一个普通人花十数年时间苦修冰系的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.20,0:04:09.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}都可以达到这个程度
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.87,0:04:11.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}而冰系妖精的话
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.33,0:04:13.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}一出生就远远不止如此了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.70,0:04:15.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}所以自古就少有人类去修炼
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.75,0:04:17.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}更别说科技发达的今天了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.91,0:04:21.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但老君不是说现在最厉害的神是人类么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.62,0:04:23.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对呀，我说的是普通人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.83,0:04:25.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}但还是有很多天赋异稟的人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.00,0:04:28.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这与灵质空间的大小有一定的联系
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.50,0:04:31.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}普通人的灵质空间大概有篮球这么大
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.54,0:04:32.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那哥哥呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.62,0:04:33.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我现在的话…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.91,0:04:35.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}大概有一个足球场那么大吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.45,0:04:37.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}也是那么漂亮么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.00,0:04:39.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}完全不一样
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.50,0:04:41.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}我的空间可是极寒地狱哦
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.29,0:04:42.41,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}进去会冻死的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.50,0:04:43.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}噢…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.62,0:04:45.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那老君的空间有多大呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.75,0:04:47.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}上次都没走完呢
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.12,0:04:49.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}其实就比蓝溪镇大一点吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.54,0:04:50.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那老君山呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.87,0:04:52.08,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不在空间里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.29,0:04:53.45,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}在蓝溪镇的背面
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.58,0:04:54.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}咦咦咦？？丨！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.91,0:04:56.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}所有的灵质空间都是圆的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.00,0:04:58.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}蓝溪镇在空间的切面上
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.83,0:05:00.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}星夜湖在底下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.37,0:05:01.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}老君山在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.70,0:05:03.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}中间是老君的四大宫
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}根据老君对空间规则的制定
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.12,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}他们拥有各自的引力方向
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.25,0:05:08.95,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}啊..
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.04,0:05:10.25,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这样啊…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.62,0:05:12.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你怎么吃掉了…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.91,0:05:14.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}感觉变保姆了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.91,0:05:15.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}对了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.75,0:05:17.20,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}小黑是什么能力呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.91,0:05:18.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}等恢复了再告诉你~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.75,0:05:21.00,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}哈哈，那小黑要快点好起来哟~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.75,0:05:25.29,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}接下来就要讲灵质空间的灵质能力和空间附属能力了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.50,0:05:26.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}已经听不懂了啦…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.58,0:05:29.54,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}那就以后慢慢说吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.79,0:05:39.83,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}夏天的晚上真是舒服~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.04,0:05:40.62,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}是呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.29,0:05:43.70,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}按老君的方法你一个月就能恢复了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.79,0:05:45.50,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}恢复后你会离开这里么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.79,0:05:46.87,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知道…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.04,0:05:48.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不知道也很好呀~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.45,0:05:49.66,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}在这慢慢想吧~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.79,0:05:51.79,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}不过以后可能会有点小麻烦哦~
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.45,0:05:53.04,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}什么麻烦？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:54.91,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}你不知道么？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.04,0:05:56.58,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}关于天明珠的呀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.25,0:05:58.75,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}上吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:03.16,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}有人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.45,0:06:13.33,Default_CH,,0,0,0,,{\an2}这是什么？
